_10.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:45:34.000Z","msg":"「如果有一日我唔係做緊自己，推我落黎！」 <br />\n領袖唔係大台唔係偶像，佢嘅權力係無，所有權力來自人民。<br />\n我哋要識得利用自己作為人民嘅權力，去監察有才之人有效地操作議會，要不被利用，我哋就要有民智覺醒，議會要懂民意，聚民心就是力量。<br />\n任何一個政府，只要失民心，我哋都可以將佢拉落嚟。"},{"pid":"4bf285901f5d35eb4291e71638cc168de8c4ad16","tid":1368415,"uid":205469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:48:08.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n時機已到"},{"pid":"2f04585e6b7747ed9d6d8d9446474396064ca710","tid":1368415,"uid":270393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:49:49.000Z","msg":"不妨一試"},{"pid":"6e0019fd58889dc7b8cc02955da6318349b19540","tid":1368415,"uid":292267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:36:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f36bc5eb3aa5ad45f71966b2c22666e0684155d","tid":1368415,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:58:34.000Z","msg":"不妨一試，不過我當初主張公投取代代議士就係唔想一拉人就收左議會皮"},{"pid":"32b7274cc2195f5eb7eef51466a7006a6073d0b8","tid":1368415,"uid":292987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:59:24.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n不要說勇武，試著說「民團」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1453135\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1453135</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8d482f42709fb5317045867ee6c1ab7d13a273fa","tid":1368415,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f36bc5eb3aa5ad45f71966b2c22666e0684155d","tid":1368415,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:58:34.000Z","msg":"不妨一試，不過我當初主張公投取代代議士就係唔想一拉人就收左議會皮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:27:35.000Z","msg":"我都唔想，但公投會唔會令討論空間收窄"},{"pid":"3329113f06e80b771e6eb110be77ab5fdfb7eb46","tid":1368415,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d482f42709fb5317045867ee6c1ab7d13a273fa","tid":1368415,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f36bc5eb3aa5ad45f71966b2c22666e0684155d","tid":1368415,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislik